Vendored version: 2.30 (single header at master HEAD on 2026-05-02).
Built JPEG-only — STBI_NO_PNG / _BMP / _PSD / _TGA / _GIF / _PIC /
_PNM / _HDR are all defined in image.c, so the binary doesn't carry
the other format decoders.

To update: re-run core/codecs/stb_image/vendor.sh.
